       <div class="wrap last">
        <div class="block text-block">
         <h3 class="block-header">
          Write to
          <span>
           Academic Senate
          </span>
         </h3>
         <div class="inner">
          <p>
           <img alt="clock" height="65" src="images/clock2.jpg" width="245"/>
          </p>
          <p>
           <span>
            The Academic Senate Chair welcomes your comments and concerns. Let us know if there are academic issues which you think should
           </span>
           <span>
            receive more attention from committees or should be brought up for discussion at the Senate Executive Meetings. Please
            <a href="https://senate.ucsc.edu/about/contact-form.html">
             write to us
            </a>
            .
           </span>
          </p>
          <p>
